# Shared Backend Architecture

This is a business-oriented application.

## Architecture principles
- Clear separation of layers.
- No cross-layer access.
- Dependencies must point inward.

## Backend layers
- handler/view: HTTP or transport layer only
- service: business logic
- repository: data access

## Rules
- Business logic must not be in handlers or views.
- I/O code must not contain business rules.
- Handlers call services; services call repositories.
